    <item>
      <title>美国邮政局长德乔伊（Dejoy</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/us-postmaster-general-dejoy-steps-down-as-deputy-takes-reins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国邮政局长路易斯·德乔伊（Louis Dejoy）已辞职，加剧了他先前宣布的离开，因为该国邮政机构希望阻止财务损失并大修其业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/us-postmaster-general-dejoy-steps-down-as-deputy-takes-reins</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 20:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
